    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the factory M Variable Differential Lock. To ensure long-term durability, the critical rod bearing service has been performed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, preserving the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While the exterior and interior show minor patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the mechanical vitals are in excellent synchronization, making it a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
